##Online Notes Sharing Portal

This project is an online platform for sharing and managing notes. Users can create, edit, and delete notes, as well as search for specific notes by title. It also includes authentication features for user registration and login.



## Features

- User registration and login
-Create, edit, and delete notes
-Search notes by title
-Responsive design for mobile and desktop devices
-Secure authentication using encrypted passwords

## Technologies Used

#IDE
-Eclipse

#Front-end
-HTML
- CSS (with Bootstrap)
- [Font Awesome](https://fontawesome.com/) for icons

#Back-end
-Jsp
-Servlet
-JDBC
-Database- MySQL workbench

##Modules

-Register
-Login
-Logout
-Add Notes
-Show Notes
-Search Notes
-Delete Notes
-Edit Notes


## Installation

To run this project locally, follow these steps:

1. Clone the repository:

   ```bash
git clone https://github.com/Sumit10kr/online-notes-sharing-portal.git

2.Navigate to the project directory:

   ```bash
 cd online-notes-sharing-portal

3. Install Dependencies
   npm install

  # If using yarn
  yarn install

4.Set up the database. (Provide instructions if needed)
5.Start the development server.
   npm start

   # If using yarn
   yarn start

6.Open your web browser and visit http://localhost:3000 to view the application.

##Usage
-Register a new account or log in with an existing account.
-Create, edit, or delete notes using the provided interface.
-Use the search bar to find specific notes by title.
-Log out when finished using the application.


